Package: cogbolt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: libcurl4,
            libjsoncpp25,
            libglfw3,
            libimgui-dev,
            cognitive-grip,
            atomspace
Suggests: cogserver,
          opencog-pln,
          opencog-ure
Description: AI-Powered IDE Core for AGI-OS
 CogBolt is a modern C++ implementation of an AI-powered IDE core with
 cognitive integration capabilities. It provides:
  * GGML integration for AI model inference
  * RWKV implementation for RNN capabilities
  * Multi-cursor editing and advanced editor features
  * Real-time collaborative editing via WebSocket
  * Integration with OpenCog cognitive framework
  * Code analysis using PLN reasoning
  * Pattern mining for codebase optimization
  * AI-assisted code completion
 .
 CogBolt is designed to integrate seamlessly with the AGI-OS cognitive
 operating system, providing a unified development environment that
 leverages cognitive capabilities at every layer.

Package: cogbolt-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: cogbolt (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for CogBolt
 This package contains the header files and static libraries needed
 to develop applications that use CogBolt.

Package: cogbolt-doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Documentation for CogBolt
 This package contains the documentation for CogBolt, including
 API documentation, tutorials, and integration guides.
